entries.femaleVariant: V? You're V, right?
Yep.
Right to the chase, huh? Well, you'll never guess where I found it – a scav haunt.
Sandra? You there?
Yeah, it's just that... well, ever since they told me what happened, I can't stop seeing them...
Figured they musta had it... but y'know, it's not like I was gonna go lookin' for it myself after...
Hehh... I keep telling myself it's over... the ones who took me are gone...
You're safe now.
I don't think I'm the right person to talk to...
Listen, you've got Trauma Team Platinum. You couldn't be in better hands. I'm sure they already fixed the sig-jammer exploit.
Look, uh, I dunno if I'm the right person to talk to about this. I'm not too great with, uh... feelings.
entries.maleVariant: Look, I dunno if I'm the right person to talk to about this. I'm not too great with... feelings.

entries.femaleVariant: It's nothing... just bring the databank to my apartment. Sending you the address now.
Thanks.
True... but who knows what the scavs'll cook up next time?
Hehe... Anyway, that's all in the past now. Got bigger fish to fry.
You wanna talk about it?
Can we get back to, y'know, biz?
Sorry, you're right. I should be focusing on what's in front of me.
You mean me – the job? Or... something else?
Glad you're holding up.
Someone's back in tip-top shape. Trauma must've put you back together in no time.
Yep, good as new. Still, if not for you, wouldn't've been anything left to put back together.
Never got the chance to thank you properly. Wasn't there someone else with you? Big guy?
Whenever you get a chance, tell him I said thanks.
You find the databank?
Sure thing.
Jackie's dead.
Uh, Jackie's, um... Sure, I'll pass it on.
entries.maleVariant: Jackie's, uh... Sure, I'll pass it on.

entries.femaleVariant: Um, yeah, about that... Jackie's dead.
entries.maleVariant: Um... Yeah, about that... Jackie's dead.

entries.femaleVariant: So... did you find my databank?
The databank. Do you have it?
Knowin' Jackie though, he'd probably take that as his cue to ask for your number and call you up for a date.
But that'll never happen, because he... Jackie, um... nevermind, I'm sure you've got a lot on your plate.
entries.maleVariant: But that'll never happen, 'cause he... Jackie, uh... nevermind, I'm sure you've got a lot on your plate.

entries.femaleVariant: Is... everything OK?
Sure, yeah. 'Course.
No... my condolences. It... it wasn't 'cause of me, was it?
No. He was killed by Arasaka. Wasn't too long after we found you.
Jackie always had too much cool to let anyone know he gave a shit, but after everything you went through? He'd be happy you remembered him.
entries.maleVariant: Jackie always had too much cool to let anyone know he gave a shit, but after everything you went through, he'd be happy you remembered him.

entries.femaleVariant: Anyway, what matters is that we're still alive... Now, about that, um...
entries.maleVariant: Anyway, what matters is that we're still alive... Now, um, about that, uh...
